When you’re looking to analyze your online business with Google Analytics, the whole process starts with measurement. This includes asking questions like: “how many people are completing your customer journey” and “where are you losing or retaining customers in that journey?” Measurement is all about collecting the right data you need to answer your business questions.

 you’ll need to package up data into readable reports that you can send to decision-makers that will allow them to make important strategic decisions.
 
